{"tid":1716860,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母是咪要覺醒了","createTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T12:50:09.000Z","uid":316802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f74f05753eda2d297c64ed1b569a07a1bbf6fdb1","tid":1716860,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:45:22.000Z","msg":"佢今日因為電話合約果啲野（支國聯通）搞到好撚嬲，不停係屋企鬧垃圾支國野，話啲19中資好撚中意cap水，仲話鬼唔望有手足一把火燒9佢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明佢之前藍到仆街，成撚日睇何志光同埋啲深藍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40f5ebf045e0be135f8c7760df1ccd9094deccc8","tid":1716860,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"所有野燒到埋身就會醒（一陣）"},{"pid":"5bb6d1f7a3f9d7f7dc3c9275c1692bb93772191c","tid":1716860,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:47:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/abpOQ16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FabpOQ16.png&h=1a9ab24c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zQHwOww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzQHwOww.jpg&h=056adf34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JerhLyH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJerhLyH.png&h=a8e9db0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"dc1f7c8aaa6d029c833b1333e984aade1448dc0e","tid":1716860,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40f5ebf045e0be135f8c7760df1ccd9094deccc8","tid":1716860,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:46:59.000Z","msg":"所有野燒到埋身就會醒（一陣）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:48:18.000Z","msg":"佢呢排都開始無再幫啲黑警口，鬧政府無能用垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d8bdba8ee77f2e3b9e97e7548223bff61ce3066","tid":1716860,"uid":300642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔係個個藍都有轉黃既機會，樓主好好把握"},{"pid":"9ba9728df3eaf1a50dc9da98ba55c226a9f8ca41","tid":1716860,"uid":316802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d8bdba8ee77f2e3b9e97e7548223bff61ce3066","tid":1716860,"uid":300642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:49:30.000Z","msg":"唔係個個藍都有轉黃既機會，樓主好好把握"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"呢排我會落力宣傳下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}